---
import ThemeLayout from '../layouts/ThemeLayout.astro';
---
<ThemeLayout page="services" heading="Content Management System">

  <section class="inner-page padd-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="svc-hero-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-file-text-o"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>Custom CMS Tailored to Your Business</h3>
          <p>Rayinfos Technologies designs custom content management systems using the latest open-source platforms, tailored to match your exact business requirements and grow alongside your organisation — so you can update content without needing a full-time technician.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-wordpress"></i></div>
            <h5>WordPress</h5>
            <p>Industry-standard quality and versatility with the latest WordPress versions, delivering great website design and a smooth user interface.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-drupal"></i></div>
            <h5>Drupal</h5>
            <p>Aesthetic full Drupal site development using cutting-edge technologies and well-versed developers that never let you down.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-joomla"></i></div>
            <h5>Joomla</h5>
            <p>Experienced Joomla developers helping you reduce operational costs, boost sales and harness the power of social technologies.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-shopping-bag"></i></div>
            <h5>Magento</h5>
            <p>Convenient eCommerce engagement models built on Magento, customised to match your store requirements and business goals.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-pencil"></i></div>
            <h5>Easy Content Updates</h5>
            <p>Update pages, images and products without any technical knowledge — our CMS interfaces are built for non-technical users.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-expand"></i></div>
            <h5>Grows with Your Business</h5>
            <p>Custom CMS designed to scale with your business — trimmed of unnecessary features so your site stays fast and accessible.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</ThemeLayout>
